{"tid":1054873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"古天奴想轉會去曼聯","createTime":"2019-03-10T07:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T12:00:14.000Z","uid":147522,"like":81,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd09d702b557031da7b2a908af27a6b65072e06","tid":1054873,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"外電消息，古天奴和不少曼聯的西班牙籍球員訴苦，他說自己很想加盟紅魔鬼。<br />\n<br />\n今季是古天奴在巴塞首個完整的球季，但是他踢得不出色，而且球會已經簽入新兵法蘭基迪莊，來季爭取出場機會更難。古天奴雖然想轉會曼聯，但對方要肯支付8600萬鎊轉會費，交易才有機會成事。"},{"pid":"ccdda07d9ceb2f814c9ac3a6a7b4b021392061c3","tid":1054873,"uid":4525,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:17:23.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"07b4554ee01557a9a35701b881403f7d9f354014","tid":1054873,"uid":142674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"尋晚踢到發哂老脾咩"},{"pid":"528c6b4354445861b531e50a88bdc555014d3328","tid":1054873,"uid":142674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋晚踢到發哂老脾咁</blockquote>"},{"pid":"38ae437fc815e32214516bc89ef05cb948d2311f","tid":1054873,"uid":37303,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"Welcome剷草"},{"pid":"b122734ead6fecc75643ef97be6dc6afb7b3e275","tid":1054873,"uid":79349,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"唔同返去猁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，緊係學owen師兄咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eccf5f5b207379630d75ff5e7402ae3c1147b1","tid":1054873,"uid":3454,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"人地獌條鋒線人才濟濟<br />\n佢又踢唔撚到中場<br />\n咪能玩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d2542471e54426d2b60d7616eaeef307b7fa68","tid":1054873,"uid":11254,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"cit